==General==

C-g  abort
C-u  num argument
C-z  undo (default is C-x u)
C-x C-e  eval-last-sexp
M-x eval-region


==Files & Buffers==

C-x C-f  find-file (Open)
C-x C-s  save-buffer (Save)
C-x s    save-some-buffers (Save all)
C-x i    insert-file (add file content)
C-x C-w  write-file (Save as)

C-x b    switch-to-buffer 
C-x C-b  list-buffers
C-x k    kill-buffer


==Moving & Editing==

C-a   move-beginning-of-line 
C-e   move-end-of-line
M-a   backward-sentence
M-e   forward-sentence
C-M-a beginning-of-defun
C-M-e end-of-defun
M-<   beginning-of-buffer
M->   end-of-buffer
C-v   scroll-up
M-v   scroll-down
C-l   recenter-top-bottom

C-j newline-and-indent
C-t transpose-char
M-t transpose-words
C-x C-t transpose-lines

C-M \    indent-region
M-^      delete-indentation
C-x C-o  delete-blank-lines
M-\      delete-horizontal-space


==Marking & Killing==

C-Space  set-mark-command 
C-x C-x  exchange-point-and-mark
C-M-h    mark-defun
C-x h    mark-whole-buffer
C-d      delete-char
M-d      kill-word
C-k      kill-line
C-w      kill-region
M-w      kill-ring-save
M-z char zap-to-char (kill to char)
C-y      yank
M-y      yank-pop



==Search & Replace==

C-s   isearch-forward 
C-r   isearch-backward
C-M-s isearch-forward-regexp
C-M-r isearch-backward-regexp

M-%     query-replace
Space   replace this one, go on to next
,       replace this one, dont move
Delete  skip to next without replacing
!       replace all remaining matches
^       back up to previous match
Return  exit


==Windows==

C-x 0  delete-window 
C-x 1  delete-other-windows
C-x 2  split-window-vertically
C-x 3  split-window-horizontally
C-x o  other-window
C-M-v  scroll-other-window
C-x ^  enlarge-window
C-x {  shrink-window-horizontally
C-x }  enlarge-window-horizontally


==Help==

C-h a  apropos
C-h k  key
C-h f  function
C-h m  mode


==Regitsters & Bookmarks==

C-x r SPC reg  point-to-register
C-x r j reg    jump-to-register
C-x r s reg    copy-to-register
C-x r i reg    insert-register
C-x r m        bookmark-set
C-x r b name   bookmark-jump
C-x r l        list-bookmarks